<lyrics>[V1]
 Pathian nih zaangfah in, Khamhnak tling kha a ser, A vel-ngeihnak in a
 thim hna, Misual kha a khamh hna.

[C1]
   Zumhnak in khamhnak nan hmuh, Nan hmuh, (nan hmuh) na hmuh (nan
   hmuh) Nanmah rian-tuannak si lo-in Nanmah rian-tuannak thawngin si hin
   lo-in, Rian-tuannak,Sisehlaw mi an ruam a kai hnga Pathian laksawng a si,
   Sisehlaw mi an ruam a kai hnga, Pathian laksawng a si, Pathian laksawng a
   si, Pathian laksawng a si, Pathian laksawng a si, Laksawng a si.

[V2]
 Pathian vel-ngeihnak cu, Jesuh Khrih in a lang, Vai-lamtah ningzah a
 huah i Zaangfahnak a langhter.

[C2]
   Zumhnak in khamhnak nan hmuh, Nan hmuh, (nan hmuh) na hmuh (nan
   hmuh) Nanmah rian-tuannak si lo-in Nanmah rian-tuannak thawngin si hin
   lo-in, Rian-tuannak,Sisehlaw mi an ruam a kai hnga Pathian laksawng a si,
   Sisehlaw mi an ruam a kai hnga, Pathian laksawng a si, Pathian laksawng a
   si, Pathian laksawng a si, Pathian laksawng a si, Laksawng a si.

[V3]
 Bawi Jesuh thawngin, A zummi vialte nih Pathian Fapa tiah min saknak
 Bia tak in an hmuh lai.

[C3]
   Zumhnak in khamhnak nan hmuh, Nan hmuh, (nan hmuh) na hmuh (nan
   hmuh) Nanmah rian-tuannak si lo-in Nanmah rian-tuannak thawngin si hin
   lo-in, Rian-tuannak,Sisehlaw mi an ruam a kai hnga Pathian laksawng a si,
   Sisehlaw mi an ruam a kai hnga, Pathian laksawng a si, Pathian laksawng a
   si, Pathian laksawng a si, Pathian laksawng a si, Laksawng a si.</lyrics>
<key>D</key>
<title>ZUMHNAK IN KHAMHNAK NAN HMUH CH461</title>
</song>